        "heading": "Roasting consistently great coffee from farms we actually visit. Just like Mike taught us.",
        "body": "<p>It all started in the early 2010s when Dave walked into Mike’s Highway 9 coffee shop and the two hit it off instantly. What began as a friendship turned into a full-blown partnership, with the two buying a coffee roaster together and bonding over their love of the craft.<br/></p><p>Unexpectedly, we lost Mike in 2025. Losing a friend and partner hit Dave hard, but it also sparked a deeper connection. This loss brought him closer to the Pacific Coast recovery community, and today he’s a dedicated advocate for addiction and rehabilitation, keeping Mike’s story alive along the way.<br/></p><p><strong>10% of every bag of Mike’s Blend goes straight to supporting the Pacific Coast recovery community </strong>— a small way of honoring the guy who inspired it all.</p>",
